<h1><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>Viewing File Info</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/working-with-files"><i class="fa fa-file"></i>Working with Files</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>Viewing File Info</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>In addition to the information contained in files, there is also information not contained in the file such permissions, metadata, sharing, and links that is associated with the file.  This shows how to view that auxilliary information. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>Show Info</h2>
			<p>In order to show the information associated with a file or folder, select one or more items in the <a href="#apps/file-browser">File Browser</a> app or on your <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a>, then click "Show Info" on the File Menu.  This will display the File Info dialog box. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="dropdown menu" src="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/show-info-menu-item@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">"Show Info" on the File Menu</div>
			</div>

			<div class="tip well">
				<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-lightbulb"></i></span>Tip</h3><p>You can quickly view file info using the keyboard shortcut: command or control + I.</p>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-file"></i>File Info Dialog Box</h2>
			<p>The file info dialog box contains a number of tabs showing different aspects of information about the file or folder. </p>

			<ol>
				<li>
					<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i></span>General</h3>
					<p>This tab contains general information such as the file path and size. </p>

					<div class="figure">
						<a href="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-info.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="File Info"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-info.png" /></a>
						<div class="caption">File Info</div>
					</div>
				</li>

				<li>
					<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i></span>History</h3>
					<p>This tab contains file and folder history.</p>

					<div class="figure">
						<a href="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-history.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="File History"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-history.png" /></a>
						<div class="caption">File History</div>
					</div>
				</li>

				<li>
					<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-lock"></i></span>Permissions</h3>
					<p>This tab contains file and folder permissions.</p>

					<div class="figure">
						<a href="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-permissions.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="File Permissions"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-permissions.png" /></a>
						<div class="caption">File Permissions</div>
					</div>
				</li>

				<li>
					<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-share"></i></span>Sharing</h3>
					<p>This tab contains file and folder sharing information.</p>

					<div class="figure">
						<a href="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-sharing.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="File Sharing"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-sharing.png" /></a>
						<div class="caption">File Sharing</div>
					</div>
				</li>

				<li>
					<h3><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-link"></i></span>Links</h3>
					<p>This tab contains file and folder linking information.</p>

					<div class="figure">
						<a href="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-links.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="File Linking"><img class="dialog" src="images/help/working-with-files/viewing-file-info/file-links.png" /></a>
						<div class="caption">File Linking</div>
					</div>
				</li>
			</ol>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>